WEBVTT

00:00:56.943 --> 00:01:00.484
and to give them a fair shot
at a healthy life.

00:01:01.195 --> 00:01:04.548
Our questions led
to a surprising solution:

00:01:04.572 --> 00:01:05.915
tax credits.

00:01:05.939 --> 00:01:10.469
It turns out, the earned income
tax credit, or EITC,

00:01:10.493 --> 00:01:14.260
is the best poverty prescription
we have in the US.

00:01:14.671 --> 00:01:18.638
The average mom gets two to three
thousand dollars a year from it.

00:01:19.060 --> 00:01:22.535
When families get it,
moms and babies are healthier:

00:01:22.559 --> 00:01:24.432
fewer depressed moms,

00:01:24.456 --> 00:01:26.428
babies weighing more at birth.

00:01:26.900 --> 00:01:31.244
But one out of five families
who could get it doesn't,